Verify_Cluster_Node_Ready
    [Arguments]    ${ssh_session}    ${node_name}
    [Documentation]    Get nodes, parse status of \${node_name}, check it is Ready, return nodes.
    BuiltIn.Log_Many    ${ssh_session}    ${node_name}
